com.google.cloud.bigquery

Class Field.Type

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.cloud.bigquery.Field.Type
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    Field

    public static class Field.Type
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Data Types for a BigQuery Table field. This class provides factory methods for all BigQuery field types. To instantiate a RECORD value the list of sub-fields must be provided.
    See Also:
    Data Types, Serialized Form
